---
title: Beefy Italian Stuffed Pepper Soup with Couscous & Mozzarella
description: Our chefs have transformed everything you love about homestyle stuffed peppers into a comforting pot of soup that’s just right for those days you need a little extra coziness. You’ll begin by caramelizing onion and bell pepper, then stirring in tomato paste for an umami burst. Add in juicy browned ground beef and our peppery Tuscan spice blend, then stir in pearl couscous and simmer until tender, with all the flavors melded together. A final sprinkle of mozzarella just before serving melts and swirls into the soup for a simply irresistible meal worthy of your favorite bowl.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/651320687f20a932d72b3c3b-44f118bd.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/651320687f20a932d72b3c3b.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/beefy-italian-stuffed-pepper-soup-651320687f20a932d72b3c3b
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
